{"id":275047,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-杭州维权人士沈炳炎诈骗案开庭，300余/","date":"2013-01-17T18:46:01Z","modified":"2013-01-17T18:46:01Z","title":"维权网 | 杭州维权人士沈炳炎“诈骗”案开庭，300余人参与旁听（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员海涛报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>，杭州市西湖区法院开庭审理沈炳炎“诈骗”一案。杭州上城、下城、西湖、江干</span><span> </span><span>、拱墅、滨江、萧山、余杭及下沙开发区的拆迁户有三百多人参加了旁听。庭审原来安排在普通法庭，但后来因到的人太多，只好改在大法庭。一个“诈骗”案何以有这么多的人关心，前来旁听？原来这是当局以莫须有的罪名构陷维权人士的一个闹剧，引起众多同情者的围观。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>沈炳炎是杭州市西湖区蒋村乡蒋村村农民。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2000</span><span>年，西湖区区委书记许迈永（后升为杭州市副市长，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年因贪腐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>亿多被判死刑）搞“西溪湿地国家公园”项目，在蒋村乡大规模拆迁，沈炳炎和当地拆迁户一起抵制拆迁，成为当地最活跃的维权人士。他带领农民多次到上海找国土资部上海督察局反映问题，并多次到北京上访。继西溪湿地维权后，沈炳炎又帮助其他地方的农民维权，当局对他恨得要死，千方百计打击他。由于长期为农民维权，没有工作的沈炳炎接受了他人的一些资助，当局便以此为名，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月将沈炳炎以“诈骗罪”抓进看守所，关押至今。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据旁听者说，法庭里里外外有很多警察，开庭开了一天时间，没有当庭宣判。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-n6WKf9KarQ4/UPgf59H98MI/AAAAAAAAZPs/Kz5UryaUVU0/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"224\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-n6WKf9KarQ4/UPgf59H98MI/AAAAAAAAZPs/Kz5UryaUVU0/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dvUy2Zs3jgQ/UPgf66t0m9I/AAAAAAAAZPw/oj_fDFaveiE/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"229\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dvUy2Zs3jgQ/UPgf66t0m9I/AAAAAAAAZPw/oj_fDFaveiE/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Zl7Y0zOBOOE/UPgf7Y3Ld1I/AAAAAAAAZP0/CEm8OxFaWn4/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"216\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-Zl7Y0zOBOOE/UPgf7Y3Ld1I/AAAAAAAAZP0/CEm8OxFaWn4/s320/4.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9UJYIclL83c/UPgf9kRSDRI/AAAAAAAAZQE/OwJr6o5YokU/s1600/IMG0116091001_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"223\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-9UJYIclL83c/UPgf9kRSDRI/AAAAAAAAZQE/OwJr6o5YokU/s320/IMG0116091001_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC_%E5%89%AF%E6%9C%AC.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}